# Task files live here.
#
# One file per task, named <id>.md, e.g. T3.md. The orchestrator posts tasks;
# workers claim and complete them.
#
# Each task file is frontmatter plus a body:
#   ---
#   id: T3
#   status: open        # open -> claimed -> done | blocked
#   claimed_by: ""
#   depends_on: []
#   ---
#   ## Task
#   <what to do, acceptance criteria, file scope>
#
# This .gitkeep keeps the directory under version control while empty.
